## CentOS 6

### 光碟yum

`mount -t iso9660 -o loop  cdrom.iso /mnt`

`cat .discinfo`

`vim /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Media.repo‵

[C6-Media]

name=6.4

baseurl=file:///mnt/

mediaid=1341569670.539525

metadata_expire=-1

gpgcheck=0

cost=500

enabled=1

`mv /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.disable`
